---
title: Harissa Spiced Beef Rump with potato wedges and herby carrots
description: The sweet, smoky, and slightly firey flavour profile of harissa paste makes it a wonderful marinade for rich red meat such as this juicy beef rump. Cook your meat exactly to your liking and serve with plenty of veg alongside for a restaurant-worthy meal.
